01:28:19.340 --> 01:28:20.640
of Congress American
Folklife Center

01:28:20.640 --> 01:28:21.940
to have hosted this panel.

01:28:21.940 --> 01:28:23.930
So thank all of you, and
thank all of you for coming.

01:28:23.930 --> 01:28:26.060
We'll see you the
next time around.

01:28:26.060 --> 01:28:27.940
&gt;&gt; Judy Richardson:
Thank you very much.

